\newlabel{tab:mech}{{3}{7}{The accelerating-mechanism axis, orthogonal to the verb axis. Downstream of beam creation the lattice transport (Xsuite/elegant) and detector verify (Geant4) layers are shared across mechanisms. The plasma-wakefield value carries the tabletop axis to its hexa-native terminus (cold-linear closed form $\times $ 1-D linear PIC parity); the nonlinear blowout regime is a GPU-heavy downstream item (\S \ref {sec:limits})}{table.caption.9}{}}
